{"tid":1606581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[居安思危] 聽日會好盛大，但大家都要諗聽日之後","createTime":"2019-09-30T15:13:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T14:44:21.000Z","uid":20099,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"99953ec4fddb8cefff25187b92070a46dc3ed729","tid":1606581,"uid":20099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:13:44.000Z","msg":"聽日六區開花 會係一場精彩既表演<br />\n<br />\n但我個人比較擔心聽日之後大家會唔會以為係謝幕<br />\n<br />\n如果可以的話會唔會出定整個十月既Schedule先會好啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命！"},{"pid":"2faac5a38bd6efc95a8758e5a531b48eaaa9d461","tid":1606581,"uid":20099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:13:57.000Z","msg":"自推自推"},{"pid":"bda4221348e59e3218360cbb36dd995d6fb81d4c","tid":1606581,"uid":20099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:14:07.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"8e052a279da1a0f6312d6396b41c51369b954f3b","tid":1606581,"uid":20099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:14:18.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"d17a887130cb4347af0917b820affb099be8cf9b","tid":1606581,"uid":20099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:14:28.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"cc1e3dc95e7b55df6550bc622c61ae3394510b79","tid":1606581,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:15:02.000Z","msg":"係 仲有105 106呢<br />\n個個END GAME上晒腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcdf59cfd7e7e57f92e355d9c4ce639c48d5aa82","tid":1606581,"uid":94915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:15:14.000Z","msg":"唔好諗住 過左再算"},{"pid":"d5cc659a57917cf071a5420ba6e74c6cfaa39cf1","tid":1606581,"uid":59693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T15:15:16.000Z","msg":"我唔想大家每次完都係比警民衝突搶走成果<br />\n外媒報導係最大既武器<br />\n但三個月都過左, 相類似報導只會愈來愈麻木<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以<br />\n衝突前有目標清左先, 唔係只係又係一日衝突<img src=\"/assets/face